<div id="pf38c5" class="pf w55 h233" data-page-no="38c5"><div class="pc pc38c5 w55 h233"><div class="t maa7 xc2 h84 y29c7 ff2 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 11 </div><div class="t m760 xe4 h35 y2aa4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 11-17 </div><div class="t m208 x7d h104 y1b5f ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE ELECTRIC SOCIETY </div><div class="t m58c x27 h5 y11a4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Apply thine heart unto instruction, </div><div class="t m88c x3 h5 ya11 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and thine ears to the words of know-</div><div class="t m776 x3 h5 y1336 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ledge.&quot; Prov. 23:12. </div><div class="t m1c6 x27 h35 y9f3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The aim of communication is to over-</div><div class="t m486 x3 h35 y141b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come the separation that exists between </div><div class="t m2c9 x3 h35 y152c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persons so that to some extent a unity </div><div class="t m14c x3 h35 y113e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is developed. This process may be con-</div><div class="t mbbe x3 h35 y141d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">structive or destructive, Christlike or </div><div class="t m370 x3 h35 y19b8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Satanlike. Each party in the process has </div><div class="t m9db x3 h35 y117b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">two functions—to speak and to listen. </div><div class="t m4cd x3 h35 y1bcf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thus there is an interaction between the </div><div class="t m44 x3 h35 y1244 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">self and the other person. In this lesson </div><div class="t m1d2 x3 h35 yea8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we shall study the receiving side of this </div><div class="t mce8 x3 h35 y1d2b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">interaction in the light of Christian princi-</div><div class="t m5a0 x3 h35 y138e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ples. </div><div class="t m2db x27 h35 y1fa9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In our modern world there is a great </div><div class="t m8d x3 h35 y14f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">barrage of attempted communication that </div><div class="t m7ef x3 h35 y1dd8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seeks to compel listening. Since the Chris-</div><div class="t mb36 x3 h35 y1604 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tian person has, by the nature of his com-</div><div class="t m1679 x3 h35 y1221 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mitment, chosen to reject all that is </div><div class="t m7fb x3 h35 y1d7f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destructive and to live by all that is con-</div><div class="t m602 x3 h35 y14f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">structive as revealed by Jesus Christ, it </div><div class="t mca x3 h35 ye68 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is necessary for him to make a judgment </div><div class="t mcf9 x3 h35 y1191 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in regard to all attempts to catch his ear, </div><div class="t m852 x3 h35 yd65 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">so that he may accept only that which is </div><div class="t m486 x3 h35 y2083 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">constructive and reject the destructive. </div><div class="t m268 x27 h35 y111c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As a Christian he must constantly ask </div><div class="t m396 x3 h35 y111f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">himself the question: What communica-</div><div class="t m7c4 x3 h35 y13ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tions are in harmony with the principles </div><div class="t m12a x3 h35 y1c51 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the self-sacrificing love of Jesus Christ </div><div class="t m41b x3 h35 y1dd1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to which I have committed myself? </div><div class="t m487 x27 h35 y124c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Everything that can be done should be </div><div class="t mec2 x3 h35 ybc1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">done to place ourselves and our children </div><div class="t m84d x3 h35 y1095 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">where we shall not see the iniquity that </div><div class="t m132f x3 h35 y20ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is practiced in the world. We should care-</div><div class="t m450 x3 h35 yf0e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fully guard the sight of our eyes and the </div><div class="t m596 x3 h35 y1379 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hearing of our ears so that these awful </div><div class="t m292 x3 h35 y2952 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">84  </div><div class="t m214 x1c h35 y1175 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things shall not enter our minds. When </div><div class="t me71 x1c h35 y141a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the daily newspaper comes into the house, </div><div class="t md0c x1c h35 y1f86 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I feel as if I want to hide it, that the ridicu-</div><div class="t m27e x1c h35 y1f71 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lous, sensational things in it may not be </div><div class="t m1c2 x1c h35 y11aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seen. It seems as if the enemy is at the </div><div class="t m534 x1c h35 y11c5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foundation of the publishing of many </div><div class="t m2e0 x1c h35 y1c2f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things that appear in newspapers. Every </div><div class="t m134d x1c h35 y1008 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sinful thing that can be found is uncovered </div><div class="t m3e1 x1c h35 y1f72 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and laid bare before the world. </div><div class="t mb67 x70 h35 y1d9a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Those who would have that wisdom </div><div class="t m9b x1c h35 yc05 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which is from God must become fools in </div><div class="t mad2 x1c h35 y1c31 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sinful knowledge of this age, in order </div><div class="t m4ca x1c h35 y10f5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to be wise. They should shut their eyes, </div><div class="t m42f x1c h35 ydb8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that they may see and learn no evil. They </div><div class="t me54 x1c h35 y15e7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should close their ears, lest they hear that </div><div class="t m338 x1c h35 y10ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which is evil and obtain that knowledge </div><div class="t mdcf x1c h35 y1541 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which would stain their purity of thoughts </div><div class="t m7aa x1c h35 y1e18 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and acts. And they should guard their </div><div class="t ma29 x1c h35 y15c2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tongues, lest they utter corrupt communi-</div><div class="t m1ad5 x1c h35 y1543 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cations and guile be found in their </div><div class="t m4d2 x1c h35 y1db6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mouths.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m833 x62 h35 y1d7f ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventist Home, </div><div class="t m517 x175 h35 y1d7f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages </div><div class="t m143b x1c h35 y14f8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">403, 404. </div><div class="t m889 x70 h35 y1113 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The special problem of the Christian in </div><div class="t m6e2 x1c h35 y1191 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the last third of the twentieth century is </div><div class="t m58d x1c h35 yd65 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that man&apos;s technological advance has </div><div class="t mb19 x1c h35 y12fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">widened the scope of the individual&apos;s </div><div class="t m87f x1c h35 y111c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">communication to include almost any-</div><div class="t m172 x1c h35 y111f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">body. We interact on the telephone, and </div><div class="t m9a8 x1c h35 y1d9e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">react to television, radio, and printed </div><div class="t m456 x1c h35 y1c51 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">media. We may find ourselves identifying </div><div class="t m407 x1c h35 y1dd1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with a statement made by the pope at one </div><div class="t m403 x1c h35 y124c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">moment, and by a youth agitator the next. </div><div class="t mde7 x70 h35 y19dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How the Christian is affected by the </div><div class="t m229 x1c h35 y1095 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">information he receives, and how he </div><div class="t maf6 x1c h35 y11cb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should assess, accept, reject, or identify </div><div class="t maaa x1c h35 y1e0f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with the communications directed to him </div><div class="t m5e3 x1c h35 y1379 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is the purpose of this lesson. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
